Mounting Procedure 
==================

|Product| supports 75x75 VESA mounting pattern with M3 screws, enabling simplified installation onto any standard VESA mounting rack. 

A VESA mount adapter is sold *separately*, if you need it you can contact us when placing an order.

.. rst-class:: text-center

   |vesa_img|

   *VESA Adapter (sold separately)*

|Product| also supports desktop mount.

You can find detailed information about mounting in the |mguide|.

